				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Tanking With Your Hands in your Pockets<a name="46239"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jun 15 04 7:37 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>as a pally I do sometimes turn attack off while tanking. You get riposted a lot, your dps is also significantly reduced from what it is from behind the mob so its not as big a loss in group dps.  As a paladin I don't really depend on weapon procs or DPS for agro. Warriors are much less likely to turn attack off because other than Incite and the taunt key they usually do depend on procs and DPS to hold agro.</span></td>
